course_description: Pre-Requisites: AEPI 530D, AEPI 534D, AEPI 536D, BIOS 516D, BIOS 517D, BIOS 518D as prerequisites or special permission. Advanced Modeling will cover multivariate methods for analyzing epidemiologic data that involve examining associations between exposures and outcomes for which the outcome data are the time to an event, event rates, or a count of events. The course covers survival analysis and Poisson regression.
prerequisites: AEPI 530D and AEPI 534D and AEPI 536D and BIOS 516D and BIOS 517D and BIOS 518D as prerequisites or special permission required to enroll.
